UPDATE spells SET summary = 'You brandish your weapon and make a melee attack against one creature within 5 feet. On a hit, the target suffers the weapon''s normal effects and becomes sheathed in booming energy. If the target moves 5 feet or more before your next turn, it takes {@damage 1d8} thunder damage. Damage increases at 5th level ({@damage 2d8}), 11th ({@damage 3d8}), and 17th ({@damage 4d8}).' WHERE slug = 'booming-blade';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Create a ghostly hand to attack one creature within range. Make ranged spell attack. On hit, target takes {@damage 1d8} necrotic damage and can''t regain hit points until your next turn. Undead targets have disadvantage on attacks against you until end of your next turn. Damage increases at 5th, 11th, and 17th level.' WHERE slug = 'chill-touch';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Choose nonmagical flame within range fitting 5-foot cube. Expand it 5 feet (if fuel present), extinguish it, double/halve light or change color (1 hour), or create animated shapes (1 hour). Up to three non-instantaneous effects active at once.' WHERE slug = 'control-flames';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Create magical bonfire on ground within range, filling 5-foot cube. Creatures in space make Dexterity saving throw or take {@damage 1d8} fire damage. Same save when entering or ending turn in bonfire. Ignites flammable objects. Damage increases by {@damage 1d8} at 5th, 11th, and 17th level.' WHERE slug = 'create-bonfire';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Create up to four torch-sized lights within range as torches, lanterns, or glowing orbs. Each sheds dim light in 10-foot radius. Combine into glowing humanoid form of Medium size. Bonus action: move lights up to 60 feet. A light must be within 20 feet of another and winks out if exceeds range.' WHERE slug = 'dancing-lights';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Create one effect within range: predict weather for next 24 hours with visible effect, make flower blossom or leaf bud bloom, create harmless sensory effect in 5-foot cube, or light/snuff candle, torch, or small campfire.' WHERE slug = 'druidcraft';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Make melee weapon attack against creature within 5 feet. On hit, target suffers normal effects and green fire leaps to different creature within 5 feet, dealing fire damage equal to your spellcasting ability modifier. At 5th level, attack deals extra {@damage 1d8} fire damage and second creature takes {@damage 1d8} plus modifier.' WHERE slug = 'green-flame-blade';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'At point within range, choose: push one Medium or smaller creature up to 5 feet (Strength save), move object weighing up to 5 pounds up to 10 feet away, or create harmless sensory effect with air.' WHERE slug = 'gust';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Cloud of parasites appears on creature within range. Constitution saving throw or target takes {@damage 1d6} poison damage and moves 5 feet in random direction ({@dice d4}: 1 north, 2 south, 3 east, 4 west). Movement doesn''t provoke opportunity attacks. Damage increases at 5th, 11th, and 17th level.' WHERE slug = 'infestation';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Touch object no larger than 10 feet. Until spell ends, sheds bright light 20 feet and dim light 20 feet beyond. Color is your choice. Completely covering object blocks light. If targeting hostile creature''s object, creature makes Dexterity save to avoid.' WHERE slug = 'light';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Spectral floating hand appears within range. Lasts for duration or until dismissed. Vanishes if more than 30 feet away. Use action to control it: manipulate objects, open unlocked doors/containers, stow/retrieve items, pour out vials. Move up to 30 feet per use. Can''t attack, activate magic items, or carry over 10 pounds.' WHERE slug = 'mage-hand';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Touch one to three pebbles and imbue with magic. You or another makes ranged spell attack by throwing (60 feet) or slinging. On hit, target takes {@damage 1d6} bludgeoning damage plus your spellcasting ability modifier. Spell ends on stone when attack hits or misses.' WHERE slug = 'magic-stone';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Point finger at creature within range and whisper message. Only target hears and can reply in whisper only you hear. Works through solid objects if familiar with target. Blocked by 1 foot stone, 1 inch metal, thin lead, or 3 feet wood. No straight-line requirement.' WHERE slug = 'message';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Create sound or image of object within range lasting for duration. Sound: whisper to scream, your voice or other, discrete or continuous. Image: object to 5-foot cube, no sensory effects beyond sight, passes through if not real. Creature examining it makes Intelligence (Investigation) check to discern illusion.' WHERE slug = 'minor-illusion';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Target dirt or stone within range fitting 5-foot cube: excavate and move 5 feet, create shapes/colors/patterns (1 hour), create or remove {@quickref difficult terrain||3} (1 hour). No more than two non-instantaneous effects active, dismissible as action.' WHERE slug = 'mold-earth';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Create one magical effect within range: sensory effect, light or snuff candle/torch/campfire, clean or soil object (1 cubic foot), chill/warm/flavor nonliving material (1 hour), make color/mark/symbol appear (1 hour), or create trinket or illusion in hand (lasts until end of next turn). Up to three non-instantaneous effects active.' WHERE slug = 'prestidigitation';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Flickering flame appears in hand for duration, harmless to you. Sheds bright light 10 feet and dim 10 feet beyond. Can attack: hurl flame at creature within 30 feet with ranged spell attack. On hit, target takes {@damage 1d8} fire damage. Damage increases at 5th, 11th, and 17th level.' WHERE slug = 'produce-flame';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Target water within range fitting 5-foot cube: move or change flow 5 feet, form into shapes and animate (1 hour), change color/opacity (1 hour), or freeze without creatures (unfreezes in 1 hour). No more than two non-instantaneous effects active.' WHERE slug = 'shape-water';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Create one magical effect within range: voice booms 3x loud (1 minute), flames flicker/brighten/dim/color change (1 minute), harmless tremors (1 minute), instantaneous sound, open/slam unlocked door/window, or alter eye appearance (1 minute). Up to three 1-minute effects active.' WHERE slug = 'thaumaturgy';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Set alarm on door, window, or area (max 20-foot cube) lasting until spell ends. Alerts you when Tiny or larger creature touches or enters. Designate creatures that won''t trigger. Mental: ping in mind if within 1 mile, awakens if sleeping. Audible: bell sound 10 seconds within 60 feet.' WHERE slug = 'alarm';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Perform special religious ceremony infused with magic. Choose one rite (target within 10 feet): Atonement (restore alignment, DC 20), Bless Water (make holy water), Coming of Age (+{@dice d4} checks 24hr), Dedication (+{@dice d4} saves 24hr), Funeral Rite (prevent undeath 7 days), or Wedding (+2 AC within 30 feet 7 days).' WHERE slug = 'ceremony';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Hurl chaotic energy at one creature in range. Ranged spell attack. On hit, target takes {@damage 2d8 + 1d6} damage. Choose which {@dice d8} determines type. If both match, energy leaps to different creature within 30 feet; make new roll. Each creature targeted only once.' WHERE slug = 'chaos-bolt';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Roll {@dice 6d10} for total HP affected. Creatures in 15-foot cone affected in ascending HP order (lowest first). Each becomes {@condition blinded} until end of your next turn. Subtract each creature''s HP from total before next. Only creatures with HP equal to or less than remaining total affected.' WHERE slug = 'color-spray';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Speak one-word command to creature within range. Wisdom saving throw or follows command on next turn. No effect on undead, creatures not understanding language, or harmful commands. Approach (move toward you), Drop (drop items), Flee (move away), Grovel (fall {@condition prone}), Halt (don''t move or act).' WHERE slug = 'command';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Attempt to compel creature into duel. One creature within range makes Wisdom saving throw. Failed: drawn to you, disadvantage on attacks against others, must save to move more than 30 feet away. Spell ends if you attack anyone else, cast harmful spell, friendly creature damages target, or you end turn over 30 feet away.' WHERE slug = 'compelled-duel';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Create or destroy water. Create: up to 10 gallons clean water in open container or fall as rain in 30-foot cube (extinguishes flames). Destroy: up to 10 gallons in open container or destroy fog in 30-foot cube.' WHERE slug = 'create-or-destroy-water';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Make yourself look different until spell ends or dismissed. Appear 1 foot shorter/taller, thin/fat. Can''t change body type or limb arrangement. Changes fail physical inspection. Creature can use action and make Intelligence (Investigation) check against spell save DC to discern disguise.' WHERE slug = 'disguise-self';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Whisper discordant melody only one creature within range hears. Wisdom saving throw. Failed: {@damage 3d6} psychic damage and uses reaction to move as far as speed allows away (not into obvious danger). Successful: half damage, no movement. {@condition Deafened} creatures automatically succeed.' WHERE slug = 'dissonant-whispers';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Next weapon attack before spell ends hits, writhing thorny vines appear. Target makes Strength saving throw or is {@condition restrained} until spell ends. Large or larger has advantage. While restrained, target takes {@damage 1d6} piercing damage at start of each turn. Restrained creature can use action to make Strength check to break free.' WHERE slug = 'ensnaring-strike';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Grasping weeds and vines sprout from ground in 20-foot square within range, creating {@quickref difficult terrain||3}. Creatures in area make Strength saving throw or are {@condition restrained} until spell ends. Restrained creature can use action to make Strength check to escape. Plants wilt when spell ends.' WHERE slug = 'entangle';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Each object in 20-foot cube outlined in blue, green, or violet light. Creatures outlined if they fail Dexterity saving throw. Objects and creatures shed dim light 10 feet. Attack rolls against them have advantage if attacker can see. They can''t benefit from being {@condition invisible}.' WHERE slug = 'faerie-fire';